<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id13aa6c97-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s215"><num value="215">§ 215.</num><heading> “Consul” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The word “consul” as used in this chapter shall mean the consular officer in charge of the district concerned.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id13aa6c98-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d">(<ref href="/us/act/1915-03-03/ch74/s12">Mar. 3, 1915, ch. 74, § 12</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/38/822">38 Stat. 822</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
